----------------------------------
Push previous state:
------------------------------

terraform state push previous.tfstate

-------------------------------
change the main.tf code to previous state

----------
Apply:
---------

terraform apply

-------
list versions → pick old VersionId → download → push → apply
                                                        ↓
                                          infra rolls back to previous state

⚠️ Without versioning, each apply overwrites the previous state — no rollback possible.

