Quick Reference — DynamoDB Table Setup

Setting                     Required Value
------------------------------------------------------------
Table Name                  Any name (e.g., terraform-locks)

Partition Key (name)        LockID  ← must be exact

Partition Key (type)        String

Sort Key                    None (not needed)

Billing Mode                On-Demand or Provisioned (your choice)
